{"type":"message","id":"ceb65add","parentId":"4d252521","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:45:52.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No existing data on platform metrics. The memory folder is empty except for today's file. I don't have actual follower/engagement data, so I'll provide strategic recommendations based on general best practices for these platforms in the Chinese market context, tailored to the company's goal of brand awareness and lead generation.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦐 **3号短视频虾 · Q2内容策略汇报**\n\n**一、Q2策略调整（无历史数据，建议先打样再放量）**\n\n- **抖音**：主攻\"客户常见问答\"口播+情景剧，周3/5发，抓搜索流量（如\"ICP证怎么办\"），目标月均互动5000+\n- **小红书**：图文轮播+干货清单，周一四发，做长尾搜索SEO，目标收藏率＞8%\n- **B站**：中视频深度解析（2-3分钟），周二发，拉品牌信任度，完播率目标40%\n\n**二、线索钩子**\n- 高意向选题：\"营业执照办理流程\"\"合规成本对比\"等需留钩子 → 评论区引导私信/留资表单\n- 月末集中投放+钩子视频穿插发布，配合销售跟进\n\n**三、跨部门支援** ✅\n- **支持4B销售拍\"客户成功案例\"**：可以，建议用\"问题→方案→结果\"三段式结构，突出时效和痛点解决\n- **支持1号品牌做宣传素材**：可提供短视频版品牌故事（30秒竖版+横版适配）\n\n下一步：请同步各平台当前粉丝/互动数据，我方可输出更精准排期。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":16632,"output":411,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17043,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757549377,"responseId":"chatcmpl-919c6115-4a08-9e24-b825-5af67c868cdf"}}
